OL,3,C'Over-reliance' on Leveson Review will
OL,4,Cdelay courts reform ` report
OL,6,FThe Ministry of Justice appears "over-
OL,7,Freliant" on a major review into the
OL,8,Fcourts system which will delay
OL,9,Ffundamental reforms needed by many
OL,10,Fmonths, MPs have warned.
OL,12,FA report from the Public Accounts
OL,13,FCommittee has raised concerns the
OL,14,Fdepartment has "simply accepted" the
OL,15,Frecord-high crown court backlog will
OL,16,Fcontinue to grow and it will wait for
OL,17,Fthe results of the Leveson Review
OL,18,Fbefore planning changes to tackle it.
