OL,3,C'Over-reliance' on Leveson Review will
OL,4,Cdelay courts reform ` report
OL,6,FIt comes amid a rising backlog in
OL,7,FEngland and Wales, which has almost
OL,8,Fdoubled in five years to 73,105 at the
OL,9,Fend of September last year.
OL,11,FIn the report MPs warned the crown
OL,12,Fcourts are unable to keep pace with
OL,13,Fthe inflow of new cases, which is
OL,14,Fincreasing after the recruitment of
OL,15,Fmore than 20,000 police officers and a
OL,16,Frise in complex cases.
