OL,3,C'Over-reliance' on Leveson Review will
OL,4,Cdelay courts reform ` report
OL,6,FMeanwhile, they are urging the
OL,7,FGovernment to set out a plan of action
OL,8,Fto start addressing the backlog,
OL,9,Fbuilding on its existing mitigating
OL,10,Fmeasures under the Criminal Justice
OL,11,FAction Plan, while it waits for the
OL,12,Freport on reform from the Leveson
OL,13,FReview expected in late spring.
OL,15,FThe call comes as the Justice
OL,16,FSecretary, Shabana Mahmood, announced
OL,17,Fon Wednesday that crown court judges
OL,18,Fwill sit for a record number of days
OL,19,Fin the next financial year to help
OL,20,Fvictims see justice done faster.
