OL,6,FChairman of the committee, Sir
OL,7,FGeoffrey Clifton-Brown, said: "The
OL,8,FGovernment agrees with this committee
OL,9,Fthat 'justice delayed is justice
OL,10,Fdenied'.
OL,12,F"Our report is a terrible indictment
OL,13,Fof our criminal justice system and the
OL,14,FGovernment urgently need to reorganise
OL,15,Fit to aspire to that world-class
OL,16,Fstandard for which the UK used to be
OL,17,Frenowned."
