OL,3,C'Over-reliance' on Leveson Review will
OL,4,Cdelay courts reform ` report
OL,6,FThe chairman also warned of the
OL,7,F"particularly severe consequences" for
OL,8,Fsome victims and their families, as
OL,9,Fvictims of rape and serious sexual
OL,10,Foffences can wait for three years or
OL,11,Fmore for cases to come to trial.
OL,13,FThe report added in the year to June
OL,14,F2024, 59% of adult rape victims
OL,15,Fdropped out of the justice system pre-
OL,16,Fcharge because research showed they
OL,17,Fcould not bear the trauma any longer.
