OL,3,C'Over-reliance' on Leveson Review will
OL,4,Cdelay courts reform ` report
OL,6,FThe findings come as the Victims
OL,7,FCommissioner published a report
OL,8,Fwarning that the record levels of
OL,9,Fcrown court delays are deepening the
OL,10,Ftrauma of victims and making many feel
OL,11,Fjustice is "out of reach".
OL,13,FMPs are calling for ministers to work
OL,14,Fwith the judiciary on trying to reduce
OL,15,Fthe number of hearings that get
OL,16,Fpostponed or delayed on the day for
OL,17,Fsuch cases as it is these
OL,18,Fcircumstances that "distress the
OL,19,Fvictims most".
