OL,6,FThey also backed calls also made by
OL,7,Fthe Victims Commissioner to look for
OL,8,Fways to boost vital victim support
OL,9,Fservices and to protect funding for it.
OL,11,FAddressing the highest number of
OL,12,Fprisoners on remand for 50 years was
OL,13,Falso among the recommendations from
OL,14,Fthe committee.
OL,16,FSir Geoffrey added: "The remand
OL,17,Fpopulation has almost doubled from
OL,18,F9,602 in 2018 to 17,600 in September
OL,19,F2024 (20% of the entire prison
OL,20,Fpopulation).
OL,26,@xD@UOU
