OL,3,C'Over-reliance' on Leveson Review will
OL,4,Cdelay courts reform ` report
OL,6,F"Seven hundred and 70 prisoners have
OL,7,Fbeen on remand for over two years.
OL,8,FThese are shocking statistics
OL,9,Finvolving sometimes innocent people
OL,10,Fwhich should be carefully scrutinised
OL,11,Fto see how the system could be
OL,12,Fimproved."
OL,14,FThe report recommended for the Lord
OL,15,FChancellor to lead discussions with
OL,16,Fthe Lady Chief Justice on how to
OL,17,Freduce the remand population to levels
OL,18,Fseen in 2019 which would free up 8,000
OL,19,Fprison places amid a capacity crisis.
